            "title": "虚拟机的创建",
            "date_published": "2023-04-01T08:46:15.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"虚拟机的创建\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#虚拟机的创建\">#</a> 虚拟机的创建</h1>\n<p>新建虚拟机</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220327234018941.png\" alt=\"image-20220327234018941\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>典型（推荐）</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>自定义</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318231302176.png\" alt=\"image-20220318231302176\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>安装程序光盘</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>安装程序光盘映像文件</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>稍后安装操作系统（推荐）</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318231421915.png\" alt=\"image-20220318231421915\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Linux</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>CentOS 7 64 位（CentOS 64 位）</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318231701504.png\" alt=\"image-20220318231701504\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>命名虚拟机</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>保存虚拟机位置</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318231838942.png\" alt=\"image-20220318231838942\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>磁盘容量：20G</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318231920872.png\" alt=\"image-20220318231920872\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>完成</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318232005796.png\" alt=\"image-20220318232005796\"></p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "虚拟机"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "http://wuhegucheng.github.io/2023/04/01/linux/base/02.CentOS%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/02.CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/",
            "url": "http://wuhegucheng.github.io/2023/04/01/linux/base/02.CentOS%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/02.CentOS%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/",
            "title": "CentOS安装",
            "date_published": "2023-04-01T08:46:15.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"centos安装\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#centos安装\">#</a> CentOS 安装</h1>\n<p>打开 CD/DVD 光驱 -&gt; 使用 ISO 映像文件 -&gt; 浏览（找到 iso 文件位置）-&gt; 勾选 &quot;启动时连接&quot;</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318232308150.png\" alt=\"image-20220318232308150\"></p>\n<p>开启虚拟机</p>\n<p>呼出鼠标：Ctrl + Alt</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><font color=\"red\">Install CentOS 7 安装 CentOS7 系统 (推荐)</font></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Test this media &amp; install CentOS 7 先测试镜像，然后再安装 CentOS7</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>救援模式（修复系统，忘记密码，修改密码）</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318232455160.png\" alt=\"image-20220318232455160\"></p>\n<p>选择英文 -&gt; continue</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318232552218.png\" alt=\"image-20220318232552218\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318232702066.png\" alt=\"image-20220318232702066\"></p>\n<p>设置时区 DATE &amp; TIME：Asia Shanghai</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318232643123.png\" alt=\"image-20220318232643123\"></p>\n<p>关闭 KDUMP 功能</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318232737541.png\" alt=\"image-20220318232737541\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318232751920.png\" alt=\"image-20220318232751920\"></p>\n<p>磁盘分区</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318232813349.png\" alt=\"image-20220318232813349\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318232949907.png\" alt=\"image-20220318232949907\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>/：根分区 </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>/boot：系统启动文件存放分区 500M </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>swap：虚拟内存分区 1024M 真实内存的1~2倍 最高8G</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318233029577.png\" alt=\"image-20220318233029577\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318233052284.png\" alt=\"image-20220318233052284\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318233115380.png\" alt=\"image-20220318233115380\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318233129826.png\" alt=\"image-20220318233129826\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318233146258.png\" alt=\"image-20220318233146258\"></p>\n<p>网络配置</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318233203911.png\" alt=\"image-20220318233203911\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>DHCP：动态获取 IP 地址，地址有租期，租期到了，会更改 IP</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Address：IP 地址（计算机之间进行通信的手机号）</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>NetMask：子网掩码，划分网段，区分网段，决定计算机之间的网络是否可以正常通信</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>DNS：域名解析服务器</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318233247528.png\" alt=\"image-20220318233247528\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318233444931.png\" alt=\"image-20220318233444931\"></p>\n<p>设置密码</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220318233512767.png\" alt=\"image-20220318233512767\"></p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "CentOS"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "http://wuhegucheng.github.io/2023/04/01/linux/base/02.CentOS%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/03.%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/",
            "url": "http://wuhegucheng.github.io/2023/04/01/linux/base/02.CentOS%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/03.%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C/",
            "title": "虚拟机网络",
            "date_published": "2023-04-01T08:46:15.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"虚拟机网络\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#虚拟机网络\">#</a> 虚拟机网络</h1>\n<h2 id=\"网卡配置\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#网卡配置\">#</a> 网卡配置</h2>\n<p>静态 <code>IP</code> ，不使用 <code>DHCP</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>静态IP，不使用DHCP</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">#IP 地址</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>Address：10.0.0.100</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">#子网掩码</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>Netmask：255.255.255.0（24位）</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">#网关</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre>Gateway：10.0.0.2</pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"虚拟机网络模式\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#虚拟机网络模式\">#</a> 虚拟机网络模式</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>桥接模式</p>\n<ul>\n<li>物理机网络与虚拟机网络共享</li>\n<li>物理机与虚拟机需要在同一个网段</li>\n<li>可用地址 0-255（除 0、1、2：网关、255）</li>\n<li>耗费 IP（IP 不能冲突）</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220320211342799.png\" alt=\"image-20220320211342799\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>NAT 模式</p>\n<ul>\n<li>路由器将一个公有地址转换为多个私有地址（NAT 动态网络地址转换）</li>\n<li><code>DHCP</code> ：动态获取 <code>IP</code>  地址</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220320211622639.png\" alt=\"image-20220320211622639\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>仅主机模式</p>\n<ul>\n<li>虚拟机之间相互通信，无法上外网（局域网）</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220320211651398.png\" alt=\"image-20220320211651398\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>虚拟机配置 NAT 上网</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220320204811328.png\" alt=\"image-20220320204811328\"></p>\n<p>打开虚拟网络编辑器</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220320204841949.png\" alt=\"image-20220320204841949\"></p>\n<p>检测服务器与外网是否可以正常通信</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">ping</span> 命令（打电话） </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token function\">ping</span> www.baidu.com</pre></td></tr></table></figure>",
            "tags": [
                "虚拟机",
                "网卡",
                "网络模式"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "http://wuhegucheng.github.io/2023/04/01/linux/base/02.CentOS%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/05.%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7%E4%B8%8E%E5%85%8B%E9%9A%86/",
            "url": "http://wuhegucheng.github.io/2023/04/01/linux/base/02.CentOS%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/05.%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7%E4%B8%8E%E5%85%8B%E9%9A%86/",
            "title": "虚拟机的快照、克隆",
            "date_published": "2023-04-01T08:46:15.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"虚拟机的快照\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#虚拟机的快照\">#</a> 虚拟机的快照</h2>\n<p>记录虚拟机某时刻的状态，随时可以还原到记录的状态（存档，读档）</p>\n<p>注意：快照尽量在关机状态下拍摄</p>\n<h2 id=\"虚拟机的克隆\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#虚拟机的克隆\">#</a> 虚拟机的克隆</h2>\n<p>克隆的前提条件：必须在虚拟机关机状态下，才能克隆</p>\n<h3 id=\"克隆的两种方式\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#克隆的两种方式\">#</a> 克隆的两种方式</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>克隆当前虚拟机状态</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>从快 照状态克隆</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"克隆类型\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#克隆类型\">#</a> 克隆类型</h3>\n<p>创建链接克隆</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>优点：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>克隆速度快</li>\n<li>占用资源少</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>缺点：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>受到母体的影响（如果源主机被删除，则克隆主机无法使用）</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>创建完整克隆</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>优点：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>不受到母体的影响（源主机被删除，克隆机可以继续使用）</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>缺点：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>克隆速度慢</li>\n<li>占用资源多</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>** 注意：** 克隆出来的虚拟机和源主机，配置一模一样，要修改 <code>IP</code> ，并且，只能一台一台启动</p>\n<h2 id=\"gui图形化\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#gui图形化\">#</a> GUI 图形化</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">#修改网卡配置文件 </span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>root@db02<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">~</span> <span class=\"token comment\"># nmtui</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">#重启网卡 </span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>systemctl restart network</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre>ps：改完IP需重启Xshell</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img data-src=\"https://zxcvmnb.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20230406194108653.png\" alt=\"image-20230406194108653\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://zxcvmnb.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20230406194124988.png\" alt=\"image-20230406194124988\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://zxcvmnb.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20230406194136771.png\" alt=\"image-20230406194136771\"></p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "虚拟机快照",
                "虚拟机克隆",
                "GUI图形化"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "http://wuhegucheng.github.io/2023/04/01/linux/base/02.CentOS%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/04.Xshell%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/",
            "url": "http://wuhegucheng.github.io/2023/04/01/linux/base/02.CentOS%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/04.Xshell%E7%9A%84%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/",
            "title": "Xshell的使用",
            "date_published": "2023-04-01T08:46:15.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"xshell的使用\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#xshell的使用\">#</a> Xshell 的使用</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h3 id=\"新建会话\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#新建会话\">#</a> 新建会话</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220320212813333.png\" alt=\"image-20220320212813333\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h3 id=\"设置会话属性\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#设置会话属性\">#</a> 设置会话属性</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220320212929548.png\" alt=\"image-20220320212929548\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h3 id=\"用户身份验证\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#用户身份验证\">#</a> 用户身份验证</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220320213002275.png\" alt=\"image-20220320213002275\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h3 id=\"连接虚拟机\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#连接虚拟机\">#</a> 连接虚拟机</h3>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220320213027809.png\" alt=\"image-20220320213027809\"></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://roger-hub.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/img_sre/image-20220320213043806.png\" alt=\"image-20220320213043806\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"xshell连接虚拟机排错方案\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#xshell连接虚拟机排错方案\">#</a> Xshell 连接虚拟机排错方案</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><figcaption data-lang=\"python\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">#1. 搞清楚，谁连接谁 </span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>检测物理机跟虚拟机之间是否能通信 </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre>windows <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> r </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>ping <span class=\"token number\">10.0</span><span class=\"token number\">.0</span><span class=\"token number\">.100</span>（虚拟机的IP） </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token comment\">#2. 如何查看自己本机的 IP 地址 </span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre>Linux：ip a </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"9\"></td><td><pre>windows：ipconfig</pre></td></tr></table></figure>",
            "tags": [
                "Xshell"
            ]
        }
    ]
}